1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:01:56,660 --> 00:02:02,860
And The Winner Is Love

3
00:02:02,900 --> 00:02:05,820
Episode 25

4
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,800
Attack!

5
00:02:15,550 --> 00:02:16,360
Now!

6
00:02:23,060 --> 00:02:24,420
[Hall of Flames]

7
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:21,420
[Hall of Flames]

8
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:25,940
[Pavilion of Flames]

9
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:36,790
Formation!

10
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:54,790
Attack!

11
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,290
Protect the Elder in Chief!

12
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:01,760
Second Elder!

13
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,440
Yuchi.

14
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,670
Destroy it!

15
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,920
Go back to the hall!

16
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,880
Guard the Elder!

17
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,930
Guard the Elder!

18
00:06:57,350 --> 00:06:58,750
Elder. Please stay here.

19
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:00,110
I’m gonna fight until death.

20
00:07:00,110 --> 00:07:00,840
-Go.
-Don't!

21
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,000
Death is no hard,

22
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,350
but the century-old foundation of Hall of Flames

23
00:07:03,350 --> 00:07:04,270
will be ruined!

24
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,830
Elder. In this situation,

25
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:06,920
they are coming in very soon.

26
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,920
What to do, Elder?

27
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,400
Are we gonna wait and die?

28
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:12,240
Except the Pavilion of Flames,

29
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,110
all other places

30
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:16,040
have been controlled by us.

31
00:07:16,830 --> 00:07:18,390
Zhusha. Calm down.

32
00:07:18,670 --> 00:07:20,440
But the result is the same if we wait.

33
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:22,110
Disciples are stilling fighting outside.

34
00:07:22,110 --> 00:07:23,880
Chequ. Stay here if you’re afraid of death.

35
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,440
Zhusha.

36
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,200
I’m not afraid of death,

37
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,670
but we can’t die like this.

38
00:07:29,200 --> 00:07:29,790
Chief.

39
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,670
The shrine you wanted is found,

40
00:07:31,670 --> 00:07:32,390
right in the backyard.

41
00:07:32,390 --> 00:07:33,110
Good.

42
00:07:33,550 --> 00:07:34,110
Abbess.

43
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,440
Please guard here.

44
00:07:36,670 --> 00:07:37,790
I'll be right back.

45
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:41,720
Chong Ye.

46
00:07:43,830 --> 00:07:44,830
Chong Ye.

47
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:48,000
For so many years,

48
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:51,450
I’ve dreamed of destroying the Hall of Flames

49
00:07:51,790 --> 00:07:53,390
to avenge my father’s death.

50
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:55,000
Today

51
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,320
I made it.

52
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:03,880
I know you’re racked by anxiety at the moment,

53
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:05,670
yet

54
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:10,110
you can do nothing.

55
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:16,550
Attack!

56
00:08:25,350 --> 00:08:25,920
Elder!

57
00:08:26,270 --> 00:08:28,040
Disciples outside can’t hold on any longer.

58
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,510
What are we waiting for here?

59
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:30,790
Let me go out and fight!

60
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,110
Wait a while longer.

61
00:08:32,110 --> 00:08:33,200
We can’t wait.

62
00:08:33,350 --> 00:08:35,150
The Hall is gonna be destroyed.

63
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,520
If we go out, we’ll fall into Feng Cheng’s trap

64
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,440
and die in vain.

65
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:40,789
We must try to delay.

66
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:04,110
Finally we are gonna wipe out

67
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:07,050
the cult, the Hall of Flames, from the world.

68
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,760
Kill all the low lives

69
00:09:11,590 --> 00:09:12,440
here.

70
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:16,910
Bury them for the innocents killed by Chong Ye.

71
00:09:13,860 --> 00:09:16,940
[Chong Ye Leader of the Hall of Flames]

72
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:19,760
The Hall of Flames,

73
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:24,350
go to hell!

74
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:28,760
Feng Cheng.

75
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,790
You fight against my sect repeatedly.

76
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,110
This time

77
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:35,640
you attack my sect while I’m away,

78
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,900
and disrupt my father’s peace in heaven.

79
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,250
I’m telling you.

80
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,350
As long as I’m alive,

81
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,800
you will never have your way.

82
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:55,640
Attack!

83
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,670
Don’t push me.

84
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,910
I watched you grow up.

85
00:10:33,470 --> 00:10:34,350
Stop crying.

86
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,690
Why did you conceal it from me?

87
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:52,030
Why didn’t you tell me my mother was dead?

88
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:54,470
How long do you want to use me?

89
00:10:57,910 --> 00:10:59,170
Since you’ve known it,

90
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:02,710
there’s no need to keep you alive.

91
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:19,230
Don't push me.

92
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:26,850
Return to Huashan.

93
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:31,640
Liuli.

94
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:36,320
Liuli! Liuli!

95
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:39,640
Liuli!

96
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:48,550
Leader.

97
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,230
Don’t be too sad.

98
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:54,880
Did Liuli say

99
00:12:57,230 --> 00:12:58,470
any last words?

100
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:00,910
She hoped

101
00:13:02,590 --> 00:13:03,850
you could forgive her.

102
00:13:06,110 --> 00:13:07,880
Liuli was a spy from Emei.

103
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,200
She said everything.

104
00:13:12,760 --> 00:13:13,590
I know

105
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:17,110
you can’t accept it right now.

106
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,470
No one

107
00:13:21,640 --> 00:13:22,840
can accept it.

108
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,760
Liuli was a spy,

109
00:13:28,030 --> 00:13:29,560
but she meant no harm to you.

110
00:13:30,880 --> 00:13:32,550
Nor to the Hall of Flames.

111
00:13:34,030 --> 00:13:34,670
She was...

112
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:39,470
She was just coerced by Emei

113
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,350
and had to do that.

114
00:13:45,790 --> 00:13:46,640
Leader.

115
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:49,690
You’ve been sitting here for long.

116
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:53,740
Let me take you back to Zhaoxue Tower to rest.

117
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,320
Just leave me alone.

118
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:34,330
Wait for me here.

119
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:05,710
Xuezhi.

120
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:17,290
Master Shangguan.

121
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:18,960
What brings you here?

122
00:15:19,280 --> 00:15:20,680
I want to take Liuli away.

123
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:26,590
Her mother,

124
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,230
Abbess Baiyun,

125
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:29,840
is my aunt.

126
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:32,080
Before she died,

127
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,880
she asked me to look for her biological daughter

128
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:35,280
and take good care of her.

129
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:36,790
It’s my bad.

130
00:15:38,230 --> 00:15:39,590
I failed my aunt.

131
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:41,350
Since she parted

132
00:15:42,000 --> 00:15:43,110
from her daughter,

133
00:15:43,350 --> 00:15:44,750
they had never met again.

134
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:46,320
So,

135
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,570
I want to take away Liuli’s body

136
00:15:50,230 --> 00:15:51,830
and bury her with her mother.

137
00:15:52,640 --> 00:15:53,350
That way,

138
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:56,200
they can be reunited.

139
00:15:56,910 --> 00:15:59,370
Why didn’t you tell me Liuli was your cousin?

140
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:03,440
Why did you conceal all the things from me?

141
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:09,080
I’m sorry

142
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:11,220
for the things before.

143
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:13,970
I shouldn't have kept it from you.

144
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:16,470
As for Liuli,

145
00:16:17,710 --> 00:16:19,710
we just met when we were

146
00:16:19,710 --> 00:16:21,440
at the Winehouse of Fairyland.

147
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:22,960
I promised her

148
00:16:23,350 --> 00:16:24,470
to keep it a secret.

149
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:28,570
Because it concerns the Hall of Flames and Emei.

150
00:16:29,110 --> 00:16:31,440
She meant to tell you everything herself.

151
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,460
And I need your help

152
00:16:39,840 --> 00:16:41,000
for another thing.

153
00:16:43,710 --> 00:16:46,880
You want me to conceal her identity from others.

154
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:50,530
Actually, even if you don’t ask me to do it,

155
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,280
I would do so.

156
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:57,400
Liuli was indeed a spy from Emei,

157
00:16:58,320 --> 00:17:00,000
but she had no choice.

158
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:03,000
Moreover, over these years,

159
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:05,560
I could feel she was truly kind

160
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:07,800
to me.

161
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,280
Liuli is dead now.

162
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:12,430
I wish

163
00:17:13,190 --> 00:17:15,000
she could rest in peace as well.

164
00:17:19,109 --> 00:17:21,240
The Hall of Flames suffered the havoc.

165
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:25,520
It can’t stand anymore crisis.

166
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:28,000
Besides,

167
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:30,160
there’s another thing.

168
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:33,110
I caught Feng Mo.

169
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,350
He inadvertently told me

170
00:17:35,950 --> 00:17:37,280
there could be

171
00:17:37,950 --> 00:17:40,080
another huge power behind Feng Cheng.

172
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:44,040
I’m afraid his attack against the Hall of Flames

173
00:17:44,040 --> 00:17:45,570
wasn’t simply for revenge.

174
00:17:46,950 --> 00:17:47,830
I think

175
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:49,920
he’ll do more harm

176
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:51,470
to the Hall of Flames.

177
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:54,690
You should be more careful.

178
00:17:55,430 --> 00:17:57,030
Feng Cheng was injured by me.

179
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:58,070
He won’t

180
00:17:58,190 --> 00:17:59,650
come again in a short time.

181
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,230
Anyway,

182
00:18:02,110 --> 00:18:04,570
thanks for reminding me, Master Shangguan.

183
00:18:05,230 --> 00:18:06,230
I will

184
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:08,000
remember this.

185
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,040
Master Shangguan,

186
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,440
if there is nothing else,

187
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:15,510
please be on your way as quickly as possible

188
00:18:15,560 --> 00:18:17,560
The Hall of Flames is to be restored.

189
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:20,160
I

190
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:22,430
have no energy

191
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:25,670
to think about other things.

192
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:31,880
Xuezhi.

193
00:18:51,020 --> 00:18:54,020
[Lord Lu’s Mansion]

194
00:18:51,590 --> 00:18:52,450
Your Highness.

195
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:54,320
The Hall of Flames was attacked.

196
00:18:54,950 --> 00:18:56,210
How was the situation?

197
00:18:57,230 --> 00:18:59,280
Leader Chong and Chief Guardian

198
00:18:59,280 --> 00:19:00,880
arrived in time and repelled the siege,

199
00:19:00,880 --> 00:19:03,040
however, the Workshop was ruined, disciples killed.

200
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,280
Elder Yuchi died.

201
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,740
The whole sect suffered a great loss.

202
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:08,830
The Workshop was ruined?

203
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:09,520
Yes.

204
00:19:12,070 --> 00:19:13,070
When it rains,

205
00:19:13,070 --> 00:19:14,950
it pours.

206
00:19:15,470 --> 00:19:17,560
I wonder how long it can hold on.

207
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:20,640
Nature takes from the rich

208
00:19:21,110 --> 00:19:22,310
and gives to the poor.

209
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:26,590
My reading doesn’t go well today.

210
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,350
I want to

211
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:30,620
consult you on something.

212
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,480
Yes, Your Highness.

213
00:19:33,430 --> 00:19:34,400
The key of war

214
00:19:34,710 --> 00:19:37,040
lies in the knowledge about the generals.

215
00:19:37,560 --> 00:19:38,800
What does it mean?

216
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,950
Roughly speaking,

217
00:19:42,040 --> 00:19:43,040
it just means

218
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:46,220
you should know both yourself and your enemies.

219
00:19:46,560 --> 00:19:47,830
I still don't get it.

220
00:19:49,190 --> 00:19:51,400
The casual talk may be an example.

221
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:54,230
The revival of the Hall of Flames

222
00:19:54,470 --> 00:19:55,880
depends on whether Leader Chong

223
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:57,950
is the right person for the position.

224
00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:01,000
Do you think Leader Chong

225
00:20:02,190 --> 00:20:03,470
is the right person?

226
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,280
We may wait and see.

227
00:20:09,430 --> 00:20:12,160
I’ll go to Dongdu for father-in-law’s birthday.

228
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:15,470
You may go with me.

229
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:16,470
Yes.

230
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:18,810
Shangguan Tou.

231
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:21,800
Did Huashan Sect suffer a lot in this attack

232
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:23,330
against the Hall of Flames?

233
00:20:25,070 --> 00:20:26,800
So many people dead in the Hall.

234
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:28,820
Maybe Huashan and Emei

235
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:31,040
are no better than it.

236
00:20:31,760 --> 00:20:32,400
Yeah.

237
00:20:33,560 --> 00:20:35,430
It’s said Feng Cheng was also injured.

238
00:20:35,430 --> 00:20:37,070
He’s injured? Is it serious?

239
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:40,140
What’s wrong with you?

240
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:42,610
How come you care about Huashan suddenly?

241
00:20:43,590 --> 00:20:44,800
No... Nothing.

242
00:20:45,710 --> 00:20:46,920
I'm just asking.

243
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:49,000
Feng She.

244
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:50,590
You don't hem and haw

245
00:20:50,590 --> 00:20:52,950
like this normally.

246
00:20:56,070 --> 00:20:57,930
Are you keeping anything from me?

247
00:20:59,040 --> 00:21:00,040
No... Nothing.

248
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:02,590
Well.

249
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,920
Let me ask you a question

250
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:06,230
If your father were a jerk

251
00:21:07,070 --> 00:21:08,590
hated by all the people,

252
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:10,560
what would you do?

253
00:21:14,470 --> 00:21:15,800
If he’s a good father,

254
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:19,070
even if people think he’s evil,

255
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,470
he’s still my father.

256
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:25,520
But if he keeps things from me

257
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:27,330
and is untrustworthy,

258
00:21:28,040 --> 00:21:29,590
I won’t recognize him

259
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:33,520
no matter how much he is respected.

260
00:21:37,310 --> 00:21:38,170
Shangguan Tou.

261
00:21:38,710 --> 00:21:39,710
I told you before

262
00:21:40,040 --> 00:21:41,170
I had my own secrets.

263
00:21:41,830 --> 00:21:42,430
Now

264
00:21:42,590 --> 00:21:44,120
I want to reveal my secrets.

265
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:46,000
So, I can’t go with you.

266
00:21:47,110 --> 00:21:49,040
Thanks for your care all this time.

267
00:21:49,590 --> 00:21:50,350
Take care.

268
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:52,590
Feng She.

269
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,350
Do you think

270
00:21:56,230 --> 00:21:57,630
family is more important

271
00:21:58,310 --> 00:21:59,430
or friends?

272
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:02,190
Back then,

273
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,690
I had neither family

274
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:05,000
nor friends.

275
00:22:06,310 --> 00:22:07,230
Now

276
00:22:08,110 --> 00:22:09,110
I have friends,

277
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:10,520
and also...

278
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:14,190
I don’t know how to answer it.

279
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:15,710
Go ahead.

280
00:22:29,590 --> 00:22:30,350
Wuming.

281
00:22:32,880 --> 00:22:33,520
Master.

282
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:34,760
Follow him

283
00:22:34,950 --> 00:22:36,430
and check where he’s going.

284
00:22:36,430 --> 00:22:38,000
Tell me if anything.

285
00:22:39,190 --> 00:22:40,280
Don't expose yourself.

286
00:22:40,280 --> 00:22:40,800
Yes.

287
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:48,040
Hadn’t I insisted on going to the Winehouse

288
00:22:48,430 --> 00:22:50,960
to investigate the Huashan disciple’ death,

289
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:52,230
Emei and Huashan

290
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:54,590
wouldn’t have got the chance.

291
00:22:55,070 --> 00:22:57,640
Elder Yuchi and Liuli wouldn't have died.

