00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,040
Any problem?

626
00:36:23,470 --> 00:36:24,320
No. Leader.

627
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,600
They were all willing to come when hearing

628
00:36:26,600 --> 00:36:27,730
our sect was hiring,

629
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,320
It’s just that...

