640
00:36:49,390 --> 00:36:50,790
How could it be like this?

641
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:52,710
Yeah.

642
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:54,120
Well.

643
00:36:54,280 --> 00:36:55,800
What should we do, leader?

644
00:36:58,470 --> 00:36:59,230
How about this?

645
00:36:59,230 --> 00:37:00,360
I have some jewelry.

646
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:01,770
Go and pawn them.

647
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:02,710
Just

648
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,870
