649
00:37:03,870 --> 00:37:05,040
as we can.

650
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:06,710
Leader. That won’t do.

651
00:37:06,950 --> 00:37:07,870
It won’t.

652
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:08,760
But

653
00:37:09,040 --> 00:37:10,640
it's the only way currently.

654
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:12,470
Do it for now.

655
00:37:12,910 --> 00:37:14,840
I’ll try to figure out another way.

