00:37:22,710 --> 00:37:24,510
Compared with your Moon Valley,

660
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:26,230
what do you think of

661
00:37:26,230 --> 00:37:27,040
our home?

662
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:30,600
Moon Valley is a desolate place.

663
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:33,930
It’s not as good as home, of course.

664
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,360
If so,

665
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:39,770
why are you reluctant to come home?

666
00:37:43,670 --> 00:37:45,710
I love traveling the world

667
00:37:46,120 --> 00:37:47,230
freely.

668
00:37:48,190 --> 00:37:48,950
Dongdu

669
00:37:50,150 --> 00:37:51,630
isn’t a place for freedom.

670
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:53,950
Tou.

671
00:37:55,190 --> 00:37:56,560
Since we've been here,

672
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:59,420
I’d like to ask you a question.

673
00:38:00,910 --> 00:38:03,710
Have you ever thought about working for the court?

674
00:38:05,950 --> 00:38:06,560
Father. You know

675
00:38:06,560 --> 00:38:08,910
I have no interest in politics.

676
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:11,360
Why do you ask all of a sudden?

677
00:38:15,910 --> 00:38:18,080
I know you don’t want to be in the court.

678
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,230
I do want you to stay away

679
00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:23,870
from the troubles.

680
00:38:29,470 --> 00:38:30,270
It’s just that

681
00:38:30,520 --> 00:38:31,850
you aren’t in the court,

682
00:38:32,870 --> 00:38:35,200
while you investigate the court affairs.

683
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:37,760
You know,

684
00:38:38,520 --> 00:38:40,980
what you're investigating isn’t ordinary.

685
00:38:41,150 --> 00:38:44,000
Neither are those people you’re investigating.

686
00:38:45,390 --> 00:38:47,190
If you have helpers in the court,

687
00:38:47,910 --> 00:38:50,470
