688
00:38:53,470 --> 00:38:54,470
Father, you mean,

689
00:38:55,430 --> 00:38:57,430
if I have the government's backing,

690
00:38:57,670 --> 00:39:00,120
it’ll be easier to do the work.

691
00:39:04,040 --> 00:39:04,950
That way,

692
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:07,150
it will ruin

693
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:09,040
the non-interference rule

694
00:39:09,040 --> 00:39:11,840
between the court and the sects.

695
00:39:12,950 --> 00:39:13,670
Tou.

696
00:39:14,230 --> 00:39:15,670
The court and the sects

697
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:18,670
are not as clear-cut as you think,

698
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:21,390
not as peaceful as you see

699
00:39:21,760 --> 00:39:23,000
apparently.

700
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,080
The connections

701
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,600
are intertwined,

702
00:39:29,040 --> 00:39:30,560
like deep water

703
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:33,850
