706
00:39:41,230 --> 00:39:42,120
You're wrong.

707
00:39:45,600 --> 00:39:46,600
The court

708
00:39:47,230 --> 00:39:48,670
is the deep water,

709
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:50,140
while the sects

